main event: On 25 May 1961, an unidentified flying object was observed over Tyndall Air Force Base in Florida, described as a round, white illuminated object that hovered, then moved slowly in various directions before getting very dim and disappearing.
interesting points: The sighting of the UFO lasted approximately 5 minutes,The object had a distinct outline and shadow,The reported movement was consistent with a celestial object under atmospheric refraction,Military personnel at Tyndall AFB reported multiple UFO sightings in the area during May 1961,Weather conditions at the time of observation were clear with 10 miles visibility.
witness description: SSGT Cecil L. Mallett, A/3C Garland L. Henson, A/3C Roy C. Elmore, A/3C Gary L. Kelly
